  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Beneta Spring Water Supply Extension Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">6km long pipe line excavation, pipe laying and back filling works, Construction of 6 water points, Construction of 50m3 capacity reservoir, training 42 WaSHCO members.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">At the end of the project, the project is expected to improve the health status of the community by reducing their vulnerability to water borne diseases and increasing their productivity by reducing time and energy spent in collecting water from far distances.</narrative>
  </description>
